metadata.name: Tulip in Bloom
metadata.description:
A peaceful moment captured forever in this stunning photograph. All in due time frens. 

Amidst a sea of flowers, one bright tulip stands tall and radiates hope. This single, delicate bloom, clinging to its stem by a thread, seems to perfectly embody the resilience and determination that characterized the web3 space in the closing months of 2022. It is a true testament to the power of the human spirit and a symbol of the brighter days ahead!
